  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">Sidebar `FilterPanel` no longer renders; results area expands to fill freed width.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Command bar shows 5 filter dropdowns (Associated Only · File Type · Date Range · Threshold · Mode) + Tags (from FR-DOC-05) + view toggle (from FR-DOC-04).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">AssociatedOnly toggle in command bar auto-triggers re-search (verify `useEffect` at lines 359-375 is byte-identical to pre-change).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Each of the 5 filters returns identical results to the prior sidebar implementation (regression-tested).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">At 1024 px viewport, command bar does NOT overflow, wrap, or degrade text below 12 px.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">PCF builds clean; zero hardcoded hex/rgb.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">axe WCAG 2.1 AA zero violations in light AND dark.</criterion>
