    </test>
  </ui-tests>

  <notes>
    The AssociatedOnly auto-search `useEffect` at SemanticSearchControl.tsx lines 359-375 is the highest-risk surface in this task — leaving it byte-identical is the safest path. Move only the visible trigger (Switch), NOT the hook body. Decision: keep `FilterPanel.tsx` file (feature-flag rendering off) rather than delete, to allow safe rollback if integration testing surfaces a regression. Tags filter (FR-DOC-05) was relocated in task 042 — do NOT re-implement here.
  </notes>

